text: Over My Head (Cable car) is the debut single by rock band The Fray off the hit album How to Save a Life (album). The single was released September of 2005. == Music Video == The video ranked close to number one various times since the release of the single. The music video was actually shot in a High School in Denver, Colorado. == Chart Rankings == In the Brazilian Hot 100, "Cable Car" was ranked #5, World Singles ranked the song #24, U.S. Adult Top 40 ranked it #2, and U.S. Top 40 Mainstream ranked it #5. == Discography == *2002 - Movement EP *2003 - Reason EP *2005 - How to Save a Life (album) *2006 - Live at the Electric Factory *2007 - Acoustic in Nashville Category:2005 songs
title: Over My Head (Cable Car)
